    • Method Detail

      • events

        public Collection<E> events()
        Gets events associated with given index key and value.

        Events are tracked only if StreamerIndexProvider.getPolicy() is set to StreamerIndexPolicy.EVENT_TRACKING_ON or StreamerIndexPolicy.EVENT_TRACKING_ON_DEDUP.

        Returns:
        Events associated with given index key and value or null if event tracking is off.
